Which is weird
'cause I totally hate teeth.

624
00:33:13,064 --> 00:33:15,568
I mean, just the texture of them
grosses me out.

625
00:33:15,602 --> 00:33:17,773
Then a career
in dentistry seems...

626
00:33:17,806 --> 00:33:20,112
