669
00:35:29,835 --> 00:35:32,074
ROY: <i>Who the hell's
calling me now?</i>

670
00:35:32,108 --> 00:35:34,146
GABRIELLE: <i>I don't know.</i>

671
00:35:34,179 --> 00:35:35,415
