713
00:37:19,221 --> 00:37:22,494
<i>but I was drunk and horny
and I didn't give a shit.</i>

714
00:37:22,528 --> 00:37:25,000
<i>I didn't know
how important it was.</i>

715
00:37:25,801 --> 00:37:27,638
<i>I didn't know
